## HOW TO INSTALL FLASK API

# Following are the steps to install flask api as a service

1. RUN pyinstaller --onefile printer_flask_api.py after activating environment, it will create .exe file in dist folder

2. Download and extract nssm from google

3. Copy nssm.exe from win64 into C:\

4. Open Command Prompt as Administrator

5. cd C:\

6. nssm install

7. Select your exe file and name the service

8. After that click install

9. Now open services by searching through search bar

10. Search for the service that you installed just now, and start the service